        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-meta">공식 발표 · blog.google · high</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Google CEO Sundar Pichai의 I/O 2026 keynote transcript</div>
          <div class="card-body">Google 공식 블로그는 I/O 2026 발표를 “agentic Gemini era”로 정리하며, custom silicon부터 models, products, platforms까지 full-stack AI innovation을 강조한다.</div>
          <div class="evidence-row"><a class="source-chip" href="https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/sundar-pichai-io-2026/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">공식 발표 · blog.google</a></div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-meta">공식 발표 · blog.google · high</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Gemini Omni 공식 소개</div>
          <div class="card-body">Google은 Gemini Omni를 “any input에서 anything을 생성”하는 방향의 모델군으로 설명하며, 첫 번째 시작점은 video generation이다.</div>
          <div class="evidence-row"><a class="source-chip" href="https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/models-and-research/gemini-models/gemini-omni/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">공식 발표 · blog.google</a></div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-meta">공식 발표 · developers.googleblog.com · high</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Developer keynote: Antigravity와 AI Studio 중심 agentic workflow</div>
          <div class="card-body">Google Developers Blog는 Antigravity 2.0, Antigravity CLI, Managed Agents, Android CLI/skills, WebMCP, Chrome DevTools for agents 등 개발자 생태계 확장을 명시한다.</div>
          <div class="evidence-row"><a class="source-chip" href="https://developers.googleblog.com/all-the-news-from-the-google-io-2026-developer-keynote/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">공식 발표 · developers.googleblog.com</a></div>
        </div>
